item.title: Logo
item.description: LOGO The git logomark is comprised of a diamond and the word git.  The diamod symbolizes how a distributed version control system works with the orange color being associated with git, a specific; a specific type of version control system.  The text associated with the logomark is the name of the version control system. RATIONALIZATION Logo The git logo is composed of a diamond with a vertical line and a diagnoal line.
